{"tid":872250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣駐港代表仍未獲港府發工作簽證　無法赴港上任","createTime":"2018-10-22T14:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T16:44:03.000Z","uid":47714,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bccbf03104632f541c451ff41b83c2527394d39","tid":872250,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2190843/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2190843%2F&d=ddV51QvMXIqpgBjBDUFDuG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1e240eda\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2190843/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2190000/2190843/4567777_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2190000%2F2190843%2F4567777_1024.jpg&h=6cd795ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣駐港代表仍未獲港府發工作簽證，無法赴港上任。（中央社網頁截圖）<br />\n<br />\n台灣中央社今日(22日)報道，陸委會於今年6月中旬委任盧長水出任台灣政府駐港機構、台北經濟文化辦事處新任處長，原望7月取得港府簽發的工作簽證後，於8月1日正式赴港履新，惟港府至今仍未發出工作簽證，令盧長水遲遲未能到港赴任。<br />\n<br />\n據有關報道指，陸委會主委陳明通今日在立法院稱，正積極了解原因及積極交涉，希望港府盡快發出簽證，但仍要看港方意願。"},{"pid":"2dc2464b5e4480a723d82fc170c0e3c6a77da46c","tid":872250,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1eec61336f3803e358e6923beb9cecf45364541","tid":872250,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"港共痴左線"},{"pid":"53f2215a923aa74eabcbf43700a81879fe8628b7","tid":872250,"uid":166766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"台灣識玩就停發入台證<br />\n到時班唔出聲中產就會屌港共<br />\n我要去台灣飲黑糖珍奶！！   林鄭可恥！"}]}